      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. It is in absolute mint condition\u2014I have totally babied this car and it looks just like it did on the showroom floor! Not a single scratch, the interior still has that fresh smell, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for perfection, this is the one. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to fall in love!",
