      "description": "Offering a collector-tier E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with flawless double VANOS actuation and individual throttle body synchronization. This specimen has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts with mechanical precision, paired with a perfectly calibrated M-variable differential. The chassis is impeccably preserved, retaining its original kinematic integrity with no bushing deflection or fluid seepage. An investment-grade example with a pristine undercarriage and untouched factory weld points.",
