      "description": "Available now is a true 'time capsule' specimen that has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. This vehicle presents in showroom condition, featuring a flawless exterior with original factory paint that retains a deep, mirror-like luster and shows zero evidence of rock chips, swirls, or imperfections. The undercarriage is equally pristine, reflecting a life spent exclusively on dry roads and away from the elements. Inside, the cabin remains in 'as-new' condition; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, the dashboard is free of UV damage, and it retains that distinct new-car scent. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the seat heaters, functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, backed by a complete, documented service history from authorized specialists. It has recently undergone a comprehensive fluid flush and a multi-point inspection to ensure it meets the highest standards of performance. This sale includes all original manuals, two sets of keys, the original window sticker, and a custom-fit indoor car cover. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands perfection, this is an unrivaled opportunity.",
